DataBase.Opration

Class PlaylistInfoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataBase.Opration.PlaylistInfoList
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PlayList, PlaylistInfoOperation

    public class PlaylistInfoList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class has information about the a playlist. It contains the music ids of the music in this playlist and controls the current playing media player. Methods for adding and deleting music from the playlist is also present in this class.
